<p>The four months of November, December, January, February: 435 posts; these stand
as a proxy of the time change.  And the remaining eight months 666.  Which would
be 333 posts per 4 month.</p>
<p>Those dark hours are where my thoughts flourish and flow.  It is the hours of
myth making and story telling.</p>
<p><time datetime="2025-03-10" title="2025-03-10">Today</time> as sunshine beats upon the melting ice of our neighboring lake, I think of
a desire of mine.  To spend a few weeks above the arctic circle; to live without
daylight.  What might that extreme tease from my soul?</p>
<p>Yet that is not this season, for upon us now is bursting blossoms.</p>

